surf kalium2 by Helix

The sequel to surf kalium


This is a linear map with more than 1:30 minutes of surf.  (when surfed normally)

It's designed for timer servers, there is no jail. It can also be played solo. After you beat the map, you will be teleported back to spawn after some special sound effects ;)

Required:

sv airaccelerate 150
sv enablebunnyhopping 1
noblock
